{"tid":81583,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[重開][遊記]聖誕節由香港踩單車上廣州","createTime":"2017-01-15T12:06:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T23:44:14.000Z","uid":67976,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dad7817b3ef75a2c6511638fffcb8cb23451e75e","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"其實想踩單車旅行好耐，只係一直都無時間同心力。適逢sem迫，又有感情問題，唔想喪飲酒咁頹，把心一橫就決定踩單車避節，上年去伊朗都係咁啦。<br />\n<br />\n本身老母唔知我踩單車返大陸，我話去露營好幾日就過左骨，hehe。之後放左架單車起朋友屋企，費事佢問長問短<br />\n<br />\n查實我無乜點踩過公路，計埋呢次既話總共淨係踩過三次，第一次喺伊朗，第二次下白泥，第三次就係呢次。真係唔知那兒來的勇氣<br />\n<br />\n由大窩口到廣州市中心都係二百幾km，其實唔難(好似係)<br />\n<br />\n朝早去完朋友屋企拎車就出發，諗住大窩口踩去上水再轉火車過關<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/zikyg631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fzikyg631&h=9a9479b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n起點<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/yez91u5r\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fyez91u5r&h=4444cddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n途中經過母校好撚感概 打返個卡先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/fnr67z1m\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffnr67z1m&h=8c2ed074&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當踩到大埔道上斜果陣竟然踩唔到要落車推一陣，其實差少少就到頂，不過人生既野...雖然未出香港已經要推車，不過其實之後全程都無推過。或者真係開始好難，過左就無野難到你。"},{"pid":"94f4ed19df30ae5c8a4ae9d1be0d2d50aeeeb19b","tid":81583,"uid":24883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hi<br />\n出快啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c00f9d5f6f811a61d1abd6eddd68d9bac2c07d3b","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:34:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> hi<br />\n出快啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又見到巴打你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第一次打遊記咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打得有啲慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"955345eaf2216ef5336aadb46f8fa3ed91687730","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T12:38:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kelnyihs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkelnyihs&h=4928e413&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好多馬騮 影果陣幾驚佢會搶我部電話黎食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/7axltw9e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F7axltw9e&h=a964f399&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n當踩到沙田果陣開始feel到啲行李鬆鬆地，落車一睇原來斷左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後即刻去單車公園買返條內胎黎綁。去左鴻運單車鋪，個老細唔收我錢仲幫我綁埋，好撚感動，佢淨係話叫多啲人黎租車就得喇，識玩呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 扺我之前每次黎租單車都淨係搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0wyuzps4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0wyuzps4&h=f2a84a3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n踩到晏晝先記得自己乜都無食過，就去左大埔食野，但真係幾難食sosad 又唔係平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔係因為呢個位睇到我部單車我都唔會食，香港真係好多偷車撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/faiowuxl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ffaiowuxl&h=41db2549&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n食完野同hea左陣就踩去上水，去到果條踩唔到單車既單車徑就行去地鐵站，拆轆入閘過深圳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/kv08mzhj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fkv08mzhj&h=b95c4626&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過到黎先發現唔記得喺香港買sim卡，唯有喺大陸買，但屌佢老母80蚊人仔得500mb，仲要我攞住張回鄉證on99咁比佢影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最少有得用好過無得用啦，感謝党<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/x9nh7eyj\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fx9nh7eyj&h=26ea6966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n見天都黑又唔想踩夜車就喺度落腳，最尾搵左間賓館90蚊人仔，諗住第一晚就住豪少少啦。入左房安頓好之後包租婆突然敲我門，問我要唔要女，我果陣嚇左一嚇，乜你咁直接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無巴打上去玩過其實係咩黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最尾落街食左好多野就返上房，反而呢一晚我唔係太訓得著，可能唔相信自己真係踩左上黎，同埋聽日就踩大陸既路，唔多唔少都有啲緊張。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ituqlpg8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fituqlpg8&h=a3aac87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二日起身食埋個唔扺食既早餐就check out踩去東莞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4523accc9b76bcd9dca14ca961cdd86e641536","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:37:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b50159b1c131233282ceddad28327b378ec12559","tid":81583,"uid":74012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"1b4a159e3e42df709a57916422974183fe6a4686","tid":81583,"uid":12510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T13:59:49.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪已經去完番黎？"},{"pid":"95f57aabaa5765b946382703c4307eb01dae3bf4","tid":81583,"uid":12913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:42:49.000Z","msg":"支持留名"},{"pid":"a0fb633c2c1ff65960d4fdc335ae62679233a999","tid":81583,"uid":42815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"a3d27b0a9f2b43959f1db5161dd08fd02af9e601","tid":81583,"uid":28250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8987564c766f3aea5a502d4a21639576f8f4f50","tid":81583,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T14:50:59.000Z","msg":"用留名功能劉鳴先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cddfb4f0dd36fa9100236fae7fcffcc9ebd2a09","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T17:08:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咪已經去完番黎？</blockquote><br />\n係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b75044fd65ba3f8a2edfe1b4fc82611d3c9f63b","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T17:08:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名</blockquote><br />\n屌你你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3e66a7462cb81ca732b87cf36a0d61cb9f9d8f","tid":81583,"uid":76412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:32:28.000Z","msg":"留名 <br />\n樓豬來回踩左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5de539bccafd69ecea808f58a0ce21043013647","tid":81583,"uid":67600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-15T19:39:30.000Z","msg":"樓豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9fc3a5ce17dda1f1a9c649726f06a4c9947010","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:20:03.000Z","msg":"講漏左果晚租房果陣佢叫我比百五 我果陣以為佢坐地起價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住佢話入面果60蚊係按金 第二日check out會比返你。我果陣都仲驚緊佢會搏我唔記得跟住食我60蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過第二日佢都主動比返我 證明我過慮喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/64mpuisf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F64mpuisf&h=65c9c556&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二日朝早就兜去深南大道一路咁踩去107國道，但因為自己幾驚行錯路，畢竟行錯路好哂時間又好難兜返出黎，所以隔半粒鐘就會停下睇下Google Map，體力去得快之餘仲好哂時間。不過其實咁耐都無行錯過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為條路都真係幾大路<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/je9zmcqg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fje9zmcqg&h=c813aebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n過橋去對面踩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影果陣後面有個妹下妹下喺度自言自語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/4e6drby2\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F4e6drby2&h=c23a3f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實離廣州仲有百幾公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到呢度為止我都仲係靠左踩，比啲車迫到踩住條白線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當踩到好想停果陣有個司機伸手出窗比個like我，果下真係好感動，即刻有力踩多個幾鐘，去到一個叫蚌崗既小鎮抖一陣。其實同人打氣只係一件好簡單既事，唔知點解去到呢啲時候係會有一種特別既感覺，好似比自己多一個理由去堅持。喺外地會諗好多野，同時亦會好容易感動。或者香港人太冷漠，真係好難搵到呢種感覺？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/e4y1t8k5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fe4y1t8k5&h=78030394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於有間士多可以買野飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為自己無為意淨返幾多水，又無特登帶定幾枝水喺背囊，忍左個幾鐘頭口渴先黎到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  即刻買左兩罐可樂一罐瘋狂隊，呢種感覺真係會上癮。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xldwr2j6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxldwr2j6&h=e841b2aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n哈咩哈咩哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dfcb71231fd66fcf0eadd5d7b165291331932af","tid":81583,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T16:41:57.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2e8dba42358cf484035d3b50cf201b70a6612701","tid":81583,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:32:27.000Z","msg":"樓豬又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9a5164602650f6a24850af3c8a51811df797bbf","tid":81583,"uid":19491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T06:44:11.000Z","msg":"樓主係咪俾党捉左？"},{"pid":"b93e5cf760df18a772d523fad978c3cbb47d964e","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T18:27:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rw5q1zvu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frw5q1zvu&h=ccbfa636&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n抖左幾個字就出發，果陣已經係四點幾所以要踩快啲入市鎮，畢竟唔想踩夜車，一黎大陸啲車真係唔講得笑，二黎因為盞暗到唔係撞到埋黎都睇唔到既車尾燈，淨係諗下都腳軟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好彩最尾都趕得切喺天黑前入到長安鎮落腳。<br />\n果陣望到東莞界個牌真係好興奮，我竟然真係踩到過黎東莞，原來單車可以踩到咁遠，唔係淨係可以踩單車徑由大圍踩去大尾篤。鬼咩，政府話推廣單車話左咁耐都係無做過野出黎，風氣又唔普及，喺馬路踩單車都會比啲van仔的士迫，單車徑又少。不過某程度上都係因為班橫衝直撞唔守交通規則既mk單車友搞串個party，怪得邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/ec8d47dd01082e97aaa1650f4eb52ec0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fec8d47dd01082e97aaa1650f4eb52ec0.jpg&h=96f35d5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n終於入到黎長安喇，但我發現呢區好似無咩野好行，就上網search下有無特別野，但結果黎黎去去都係講酒店小姐質素、揼骨邊間好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我就知今晚除左食下野就無咩好做<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/804tzhqu\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F804tzhqu&h=6197bfa0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n搵左間48蚊既賓館住。入去果陣個老闆見我著住單車百萬行既衫就以為我係成隊人咁出發，真係不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過講真，自己一個踩其實感受更深，諗多好多野，各有各好啦。呢間環境係無第一日咁好架喇，但真係平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過其實青旅仲更加平，只係果陣懶得搵，又唔肯定有無，所以就求其有得住就算喇。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/91ioazcy\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F91ioazcy&h=962690fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n整頓完啲野就落街行左一陣。附近真係無咩野好行，係得一個大少少既商場同廣場，一堆大媽喺度跳舞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到我返上樓諗住沖涼果陣就中伏喇，除哂衫滿心歡喜沖個熱水涼，仆你個街無熱水既喂！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我即刻落去搵老闆理論，佢話咁岩今日無熱水，凍水都得架姐。痴線架咩果陣得十幾度咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣我就知我同佢既世界唔同，佢係西伯利亞人，而繼續講亦唔會變到熱水出黎，所以唯有返上去用凍水洗左個頭，抹下身就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 慳返啖氣暖下肚好過喇，果陣既我真係無錢無女無熱水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b9be7ac06b353f7945731a6f4cf4e56bdb9df42","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T18:47:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓豬又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要我一日仲在生，一日都唔會爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0fdc622abbf1fb06008a70e939f2f675177a74","tid":81583,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T19:55:54.000Z","msg":"係大陸踩單車一定要帶面罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be5b26dadea36e9942ed5e80636b96e458dbe2b6","tid":81583,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T03:04:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要我一日仲在生，一日都唔會爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d出文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09b7df925ea6e6d2383070624683c8a1d39f38f","tid":81583,"uid":49868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T08:49:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要我一日仲在生，一日都唔會爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有拖無欠咁話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543c1ad9473596560f4747e90d030464441e6e6a","tid":81583,"uid":63177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T09:23:39.000Z","msg":"留名 快d寫"},{"pid":"661f5c6f79e4a64aec643fad258ed1eb30c24ffd","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/05rkeux3\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F05rkeux3&h=a8df5459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n求其揀左間有野食既就入左去，其實成間鋪入面得自己一個客喺度食野既感覺真係好奇怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似阻緊人收工咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最尾食左個廿蚊叉雞飯，佢話可以免費加多碗聲稱係用藥材煲既湯，咁就幾歹都試下啦，黎到飲落其實幾重味精味，但喺大陸唔講究得咁多，食你唔死既就叫做食物<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qdmfsnt4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqdmfsnt4&h=348b6965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n無謂再騷擾你 我沒這塊厚面皮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/qdmfsnt4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fqdmfsnt4&h=348b6965&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好耐無見過大牛龜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 就喺我諗緊唔知自己睇緊乜既時候，我個fd wtsapp我話出左grade，仲話佢過3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 明明佢就炒左exam.. group啲人仲係咁喺度講邊科無a得a-咋我真係想衝返香港向佢跪低，求佢唔好再講落去。。。果陣既我其實知自己唔會過3架喇，所以心情真係灰到極點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後諗住訓覺訓醒就無野繼續出發，但房入面隻蚊搞到我成晚無覺好訓，不斷扎醒、掙扎、扎醒、掙扎，但胡師父唔喺度我都無力掙扎，所以最尾重覆到大約兩三點就訓著左，但九點就要起身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n朝早起身果陣發現額頭比蚊咬過，出到街我幾驚啲人會以為我係家燕媽媽個仔。。。最尾攞啲陰遮遮佢，希望無人發覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2jzi4b6f\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2jzi4b6f&h=c1305ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n落樓下食埋個早餐就check out，幾樣野加埋先十四蚊咋，喺香港十四蚊都未必買到一碗粥，我愛地溝油！<br />\n過去兩日都係自己踩，估唔到今日就遇到貴人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6e8853052fd6f4bb0fc998498bda67031fd1839","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:53:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係大陸踩單車一定要帶面罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果幾日我都唔知吸左幾多無害既有毒氣體"},{"pid":"394e986dd445dfa0b478e6d60acc8ef3f6ce31db","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓豬又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要我一日仲在生，一日都唔會爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有拖無欠咁話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個就梗架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3f298a4e43bd6be221eac39969e33b0c3ecbca9","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-21T15:55:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名 快d寫</blockquote><br />\n多謝g持 每一個留言就係我出文既動力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc7c66c69807b39742ae6942ec6401e6e98034ba","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:49:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710047b11982cebafd263ec430d3c55fdbc64b5c","tid":81583,"uid":53578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-22T01:49:50.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"a4f7ea8296ddccb2ac247ed7d84c2436f0072299","tid":81583,"uid":44066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T10:28:15.000Z","msg":"留名等update<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7399c9aa7e732a4cc5165f08f0108213f832514","tid":81583,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:15:59.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"80526abcce706d7d63ccffa34cbfd36b466c71e6","tid":81583,"uid":53876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:22:37.000Z","msg":"我都試過踩上廣州，不過係落馬洲出發<br />\n踩完啲鼻屎係黑色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBtw中學同樓主同一間學校"},{"pid":"1bec1e9ca5003b130556d33dc86be7ad0cfec2b2","tid":81583,"uid":70092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:23:34.000Z","msg":"屌你老母唔係唔想撐你<br />\n但係你十鳩幾日先出一篇會唔會太摟屌？"},{"pid":"8d6737eb7cdd5e9bdb584eb65d85fe4b6722f637","tid":81583,"uid":25659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:42:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你老母唔係唔想撐你<br />\n但係你十鳩幾日先出一篇會唔會太摟屌？</blockquote><br />\n好誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一開始隔左成個月先出文<br />\n想人點追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a62bee3fc94ad096319cc5bfefcf6c7570495a68","tid":81583,"uid":78105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-27T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"留名想睇踩大陸路會點"},{"pid":"6004591e0ed6007d39450a9f10b41595bd445819","tid":81583,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:26:33.000Z","msg":"樓豬幾時先肯寫埋佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be40dfc25170fd91497be67bec31cdc5fd3ad934","tid":81583,"uid":54028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T03:29:31.000Z","msg":"尾已爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bbfce0de9c5af4163f46165fbfbb025ff34697a","tid":81583,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T15:56:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"70121a998245078935b849acea76c3c9f5c4a033","tid":81583,"uid":34295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T03:03:32.000Z","msg":"屌咩"},{"pid":"00c6ef42925b78b332399b5fddcf6bd47386bed6","tid":81583,"uid":25164,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T09:46:41.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"cad83afb6c74dc65aea546956d719147ae36d7c6","tid":81583,"uid":65984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-17T12:06:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓豬又爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n只要我一日仲在生，一日都唔會爛尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55bcc9d18cc78f433d9fc13adfba4830ed1aaffa","tid":81583,"uid":66683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-22T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"44208431c09f6d37dc5ffb920540eee347b9c817","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:52:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食完早餐check out就沿住德政中路踩返去107國道。當踩到去大嶺山鎮果邊就開始多大型重型貨車，每踩幾分鐘就會塞一次。由於啲重型車就喺我隔離線，本身仲有少少位淨既變到得返岩岩好夠一架單車過，仲要係要踩喺坑渠上面，不過唔係左搖右擺咁踩既話都唔係咩大問題。但當佢地塞完車再行既時候又會繼續呠你，眾所鳩知大型貨車響咹係特別大聲，再加埋佢地喺你旁邊駛過，自己又要keep住踩，我而家諗返起都虎驅一震。<br />\n<br />\n踩多半個鐘之後見到有段路有工人喺度油緊油，但又無圍欄圍住唔比過，當時又無為意就就咁踩過去。踩過左之後先發現啲油未乾哂，我半個轆都係啲白油，諗返起真係唔多好意思，sor9ly<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 果陣覺得成條駄白哂好柒，不過踩到入東莞市中心啲油都已經甩得七七八八。遺憾係入到黎東莞市中心都無認真留過喺度，一味係咁踩就過左了:( <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/adc8ezsh\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fadc8ezsh&h=bda112bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實踩到返香港都仲有少少油喺度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n踩到近中堂鎮發現有大叔喺行人路賣緊木製軍事武器，本來我就無停低就咁踩過左，但諗諗下好似幾有趣就特登踩返返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 個呀叔見我有興趣就話：咱們祖國強大了，美國不是我們的對手！我：55。然後就揀左架坦克車做紀念，買左30蚊人仔，其實幾貴。佢話仲有好多款式，我就話一架就夠，不了<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/8d21m0qf\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F8d21m0qf&h=c307fc3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/v2n0gx83\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fv2n0gx83&h=45b498c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踩到大約四點就到廣州橋，見有少少攰個景又幾靚就抖下。條橋其實好鬼震，震過荃灣新開果條天橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過其實正常既，一條橋咁多重型貨車唔震先要驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/3k6nvgo8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F3k6nvgo8&h=4097319c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0u12cxtp\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0u12cxtp&h=080cb8e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n抖抖下就有一個大叔踩單車經過，撩我問我喺度做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cd3edd6f4d4bb0b74f302983c61d8e063444936","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:54:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0h7ps53t\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0h7ps53t&h=735798d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n補返上面大牛龜張相"},{"pid":"6c6ac04c00c39fc417e30838352588f66707cedd","tid":81583,"uid":64716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T20:31:47.000Z","msg":"其實每晚都有單車團上惠州 或 珠海廣州<br />\n而且都幾pro.  你唔熟就冇計，其實100蚊左右o既hostel都ok .不過都係要join member網上book.    電話卡而家聯通4g  1蚊500mb , 用到你唔用啦。<br />\nanyway行g107 真係小心o的，好易變肉醬。"},{"pid":"1e6937572d06bbeb616f0fd3d252a4311cb68628","tid":81583,"uid":43720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T05:29:48.000Z","msg":"終於更新了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d742a6b86d46c859cdc8c62c0a8f1a3e9c6f043c","tid":81583,"uid":43119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"完？"},{"pid":"0939b1f5ffff6365b7f86d3f57c7379a09aea824","tid":81583,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T15:57:49.000Z","msg":"其實見到陌生人主動問我野會有啲戒心。大陸喎，由細到大都覺得大陸人好冷血同無乜好人，一個充滿危險既地獄鬼國。不過見佢個樣幾老實年紀又唔細，斷估都唔會賣我豬仔既。<br />\n<br />\n佢見我咁大袋行李就問我喺邊度踩過黎，我照直答香港，先知原來佢都曾經喺香港住過6年，只係掛住大陸既農村生活先搬返返黎長住。佢話佢住喺香港果排佢日日都以單車代步，已經踩左單車好多年。佢仲同我講喺大陸如果識得行小路既話會慳好多時間，大路其實兜好多路又多車，啲廢氣真係唔講得笑。佢之後提議話可以帶一帶我踩小路去黃埔果邊，如果踩大路會好哂時間。喺呢一刻雖然好興奮有人帶路，但始終少黎大陸點都會驚驚地。不過果陣又諗既然都豁左出去單機踩上黎，就唔爭在啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/ATZNanr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FATZNanr&h=b1981fb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我一路跟住佢後面，佢比我平時踩得慢好多。一黎佢都幾廿歲人喇，賽跑冠軍都係幾廿年前既事，二黎佢部車其實好舊，連有無得轉波都成問題。我問佢點解唔換過另一部單車？佢話部車已經踩左十幾年有感情，加上又未壞就唔想換喇。果然上一代都係長情啲。<br />\n<br />\n到佢帶到去小路果陣先醒起呢度仍然係鄉村地方，小路即係off-road，成條路都係碎石路黎。好彩本身踩mtb上黎，如果唔係都唔知要爆幾多次駄喇，所以喺時間同安全之間點都會有trade-off。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/XhM0H9y\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FXhM0H9y&h=159ed534&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/GG5whbe\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FGG5whbe&h=32ca903a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺廣州另一邊望返返去東莞真係有另一番感受<br />\n<br />\n到左黃埔區我就同佢分道揚鑣，佢返屋企煮飯，我就搵左間好少少既酒店。原本想特登dl wechat同佢保持聯絡，但仲未接受到用呢啲國產app就打消左呢個念頭，依依不捨同佢道別。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgur.com/VXncbDr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgur.com%2FVXncbDr&h=30d636e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本身仲覺得百幾蚊一晚酒店都唔算平，但當住過香港同台灣果啲就知大陸啲酒店真係世界級咁平，不過我都係唔敢用佢比既毛巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然而家都係保持觀望態度，要我再上大陸都仍然會好謹慎，但至少無我想像中咁不堪，或者好多時真係要靠自己探索呢個世界。由其是伊朗，仍然有好多人以為伊朗日日都打仗，到處都係isis分子同土製炸彈。<br />\n<br />\n有時會覺得緣份呢樣野真係好奇妙。如果唔係我停喺度抖，我唔會遇到呢個大叔，令我覺得大陸真係有好人；如果唔係上年無聊開post相認，我根本就唔會識到你，未必會有呢個遊記出現。<br />\n<br />\n就好似天與地入面如果呀Yan肯返轉頭原諒家明，家明就唔會去天山就唔洗死，中間就唔會發生咁多野，結局會變得好唔同。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我知而家無人睇架喇，拖下拖下竟然拖下今年聖誕咁濟，連啲圖都死哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都知自己開左好多空頭支票，唔好嬲啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實都差唔多完lu。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 估唔到咁就差唔多一年"}]}